---
title: Golden Roast Chicken & Paella-Style Risoni with Chorizo & Lemon-Parsley Dressing
description: Paella originated out of the beautiful city of Valencia in Spain and since then it’s been a near impossible task to identify what goes into a paella. So let’s try out our own take on this fan-favourite with a smokey roasted half chicken resting on saucy risoni. Drizzle over the zesty parsley dressing to elevate those flavours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/golden-roast-chicken-paella-style-risoni-5f6408bf.jpg
